{"tid":2238112,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"焦點燃論—宣道老師終身「釘牌」  教育界遭文革式清算  蘋果日報","createTime":"2020-10-11T00:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T00:47:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b961098b107f75c7388f484442e0358e9a6d92a4","tid":2238112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T00:47:48.000Z","msg":"#宣道 #教育局 #Appledaily<br />\n<br />\n焦點燃論&mdash;宣道老師終身「釘牌」 <br />\n教育界遭文革式清算 <br />\n蘋果日報 Apple Daily<br />\n&mdash;20201009<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4Y8bs0099Kk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4Y8bs0099Kk&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=ee8aa97d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4Y8bs0099Kk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.73M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n教育局以涉嫌宣揚「港獨」為由，出手取消九龍塘宣道小學一名教師註冊，是首宗涉及專業失德和問題教材而被取消教師註冊的個案，但有關教師未獲答辯機會，教育局更警告，若再發生同類事件，將會與保安局等執法機關共同跟進；教協批未予教師答辯下施以「極刑」不合理，會助「釘牌」教師上訴。<br />\n<br />\n北京一直將香港的社會運動歸咎於特區的教育工作有所不足，身兼全國政協副主席的前特首梁振英更不時追擊教育界。「港版國安法」之下，香港教育界是否已成北京整頓目標？教師會否接連面對無理的文革式清算？教師往後制訂教案時，會有甚麼影響？香港仍然擁有學術討論自由嗎？今集《焦點燃論》請來教育界立法會議員葉建源及前通識科教師楊子俊為大家分析。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=2c909200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=679e0588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=b40302c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone</a><br />\nAndroid App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-Android&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=4a700b05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android</a><br />\n======="}]}